   You are babysitting three cousins.  You treat them to a meal at the 
   Golden Arches.  You are going to need a cup of coffee if you are to 
   get through this.  
   Write a program that will calculate the cost of three Happy Meals, 
   priced at $4.95 each.   
   The coffee is $1.27.   Display your answer in a simple sentence:  

   "The cost of three Happy Meals and a coffee is xxxxx." 
